cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: Single-Party Framework Agreement in Seven Lots for the Managed Supply of Food, Beverages and Catering Consumables
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: The Contracting Authority intends to establish seven single-party framework agreements for the managed supply of food, beverages and catering consumables. The successful framework member under each lot of the competition will be required to assist the Contracting Authority in monitoring and managing the usage of stock, to include assisting with initiatives intended to minimise wastage and ensure the efficient usage of perishable products. Full information regarding the Contracting Authority's requirements is contained in the Invitation to Tender document, available to download from www.etenders.gov.ie.
